                            <h1><strong>Application</strong></h1>
<br/>
Please visit our <a href="https://www.theigc.org/funding/call-for-proposals" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">website</a> to read the full guidance and instructions on how to apply. Here, you can also find <a href="https://www.theigc.org/funding/call-for-proposals/resources-applicants" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">additional resources for applicants</a>.
